White and pink Ume plum blossoms are starting to appear at Seiryo-ji temple and elsewhere around town.
</p>
<p class="jp">
清涼寺や街のあちこちで、白やピンクの梅の花が咲き始めている。

</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Temples" /><category term="Flowers" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[White and pink Ume plum blossoms are starting to appear at Seiryo-ji temple and elsewhere around town. 清涼寺や街のあちこちで、白やピンクの梅の花が咲き始めている。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_DSCF1693_edit.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_DSCF1693_edit.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Mangan-ji・満願寺</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260212/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Mangan-ji・満願寺" /><published>2026-02-12T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-02-12T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/manganji</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260212/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
The <em>sanmon</em> (entrance gate) of this Buddhist temple in Okazaki, with its elegant tiled roof and traditional wooden plaque. Through the gateway, the temple grounds and buildings are visible beyond.
</p>
<p class="jp">
岡崎にある仏教寺院の山門。美しい瓦屋根と伝統的な扁額が特徴。

</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Higashiyama" /><category term="Temples" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The sanmon (entrance gate) of this Buddhist temple in Okazaki, with its elegant tiled roof and traditional wooden plaque. Through the gateway, the temple grounds and buildings are visible beyond. 岡崎にある仏教寺院の山門。美しい瓦屋根と伝統的な扁額が特徴。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_DSCF1676.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_DSCF1676.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Hi-Key Bamboo・ハイキーの竹</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260211/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Hi-Key Bamboo・ハイキーの竹" /><published>2026-02-11T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-02-11T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/bamboo</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260211/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
The bamboo grove, lit from the side by the afternoon sun. It made for a nice contrasty look.
</p>
<p class="jp">
午後の太陽に横から照らされた竹林。コントラストが美しい。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Bamboo Grove" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The bamboo grove, lit from the side by the afternoon sun. It made for a nice contrasty look. 午後の太陽に横から照らされた竹林。コントラストが美しい。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03475_edit-2.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03475_edit-2.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Kamogawa River・鴨川</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260210/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Kamogawa River・鴨川" /><published>2026-02-10T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-02-10T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/kamo-snow</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260210/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
The remaining snow shines in the morning sun. 
</p>
<p class="jp">
残雪が朝日を浴びて輝いている。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Kamo River" /><category term="Snow" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[The remaining snow shines in the morning sun. 残雪が朝日を浴びて輝いている。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03439.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03439.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Bridge &amp;amp; Pine・橋と松</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260209/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Bridge &amp;amp; Pine・橋と松" /><published>2026-02-09T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-02-09T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/bridge+pine</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260209/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
A pine tree frames Arashiyama’s Togetsu Bridge in the snow.
</p>
<p class="jp">
松の木が雪の嵐山渡月橋を縁取る。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Katsura River" /><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><category term="Snow" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[A pine tree frames Arashiyama’s Togetsu Bridge in the snow. 松の木が雪の嵐山渡月橋を縁取る。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03378_edit.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03378_edit.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Katsura River in Snow・雪の桂川</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260208/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Katsura River in Snow・雪の桂川" /><published>2026-02-08T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-02-08T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/snow</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260208/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Snow turns Arashiyama into a canvas of black and white, like a Sumi-e ink painting.
</p>
<p class="jp">
雪が降ると、嵐山は墨絵のような白黒の世界に変わる。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Katsura River" /><category term="Togetsu Bridge" /><category term="Snow" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Snow turns Arashiyama into a canvas of black and white, like a Sumi-e ink painting. 雪が降ると、嵐山は墨絵のような白黒の世界に変わる。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03364_edit-1.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03364_edit-1.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Joshua Breakstone</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260207/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Joshua Breakstone" /><published>2026-02-07T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-02-07T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/joshua-breakstone</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260207/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Jazz guitarist Joshua Breakstone performing at <a href="https://bondsrosary.com" target="_blank">Bond's Rosary</a> in Gion. 
</p>
<p class="en">
I had to move as far back as I could to fit him into the view of my 50mm lens, but I liked what of all the out of focus elements on my table added to the picture.

</p>
<p class="jp">
ジャズ・ギタリスト、ジョシュア・ブレークストーンが祇園の<a href="https://bondsrosary.com" target="_blank">ボンズ・ロザリー</a>で演奏している。
</p>
<p class="jp">
50mmレンズの視界に彼を収めるため、かなり後ろに下がる必要があったが、テーブル上のボケた物たちが写真に良いアクセントになった。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Concerts" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Jazz guitarist Joshua Breakstone performing at Bond's Rosary in Gion. I had to move as far back as I could to fit him into the view of my 50mm lens, but I liked what of all the out of focus elements on my table added to the picture.]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03329_edit.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03329_edit.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">River Pine・川の松</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260206/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="River Pine・川の松" /><published>2026-02-06T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-02-06T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/river-pine</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260206/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
A pine tree along the Oi River, bathed in morning light. 
</p>
<p class="jp">
大堰川の岸辺の松が朝の光を浴びている。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Arashiyama" /><category term="Katsura River" /><category term="Foliage" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[A pine tree along the Oi River, bathed in morning light. 大堰川の岸辺の松が朝の光を浴びている。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03263_edit.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03263_edit.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Umezono・梅園</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260205/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Umezono・梅園" /><published>2026-02-05T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-02-05T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/umezono</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260205/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Retro Showa Era elegance of this sweets shop in the Teramachi shopping arcade.
</p>
<p class="jp">
寺町商店街に佇む老舗甘味処・梅園の風情ある佇まい。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Architecture" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Retro Showa Era elegance of this sweets shop in the Teramachi shopping arcade. 寺町商店街に佇む老舗甘味処・梅園の風情ある佇まい。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03222.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03222.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry><entry><title type="html">Kurumazaki Jinja・車折神社</title><link href="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260204/" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="Kurumazaki Jinja・車折神社" /><published>2026-02-04T00:00:00+09:00</published><updated>2026-02-04T00:00:00+09:00</updated><id>https://hermosawavephotography.com/kurumazaki-jinja</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://hermosawavephotography.com/260204/"><![CDATA[<p class="en">
Looking thru the Shimmon Gate at Kurmazaki Jinja shrine, as daylight fades.
</p>
<p class="jp">
日が暮れゆく中、車折神社の神門越しに眺める。
</p>]]></content><author><name>Daniel Sofer</name></author><category term="Kyoto" /><category term="Shrines" /><category term="Dusk" /><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Looking thru the Shimmon Gate at Kurmazaki Jinja shrine, as daylight fades. 日が暮れゆく中、車折神社の神門越しに眺める。]]></summary><media:thumbnail xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03252_edit.jpg" /><media:content medium="image" url="https://hermosawavephotography.com/assets/images/2026/2602_A7R03252_edit.jpg" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" /></entry></feed>